OL,3,CCall for fair, ambitious climate plan
OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,FThe UK's world-leading climate law has
OL,7,Fhad a "transformative" effect on
OL,8,Ffighting global warming, but progress
OL,9,Fis now at risk, a report warns.
OL,11,FIn a report launched to mark the 16th
OL,12,Fanniversary of the UK's world-first
OL,13,FClimate Change Act, campaign group
OL,14,FFriends of the Earth warns the
OL,15,Fpolitical consensus around climate
OL,16,Faction is unravelling, even as
OL,17,Fbusiness leaders say it drives
OL,18,Feconomic growth.
