OL,3,CCall for fair, ambitious climate plan
OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,FAfter what Friends of the Earth
OL,7,Fdescribes as "climate delays and U-
OL,8,Fturns" by the last government, the UK
OL,9,Fis off track to meet targets under the
OL,10,FAct to cut emissions in the 2030s, and
OL,11,Fto achieve an international pledge to
OL,12,Fslash the pollution driving rising
OL,13,Ftemperatures by 68% by 2030.
