OL,3,CCall for fair, ambitious climate plan
OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,FAnd while the Labour Government has
OL,7,Fpositioned itself as a climate leader,
OL,8,Fanalysis by the green group suggests
OL,9,Fthat, since the general election,
OL,10,Fthere has been limited delivery on the
OL,11,F10 urgent asks by the independent
OL,12,Fadvisory Climate Change Committee to
OL,13,Fget the UK back on track.
OL,15,FWith climate action plans by the
OL,16,Fprevious government being judged
OL,17,Funlawful, and a new plan required by
OL,18,FMay 2025, Friends of the Earth is
OL,19,Furging ministers to set out a credible
OL,20,Fand fair new plan for climate action.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
