OL,3,CCall for fair, ambitious climate plan
OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,FIt must fairly finance action from a
OL,7,Flocal to international level; ensure
OL,8,Feveryone can live in warm homes with
OL,9,Fclean, cheap energy; deliver
OL,10,Faffordable reliable public transport
OL,11,Ffor all; and help people find good
OL,12,Fgreen jobs, particularly for sectors
OL,13,Fand areas at risk of being left
OL,14,Fbehind, the group says.
