OL,3,CCall for fair, ambitious climate plan
OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,FBut progress stalled under the
OL,7,Fgovernment led by Rishi Sunak, while
OL,8,Fnew Conservative leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,9,Fhas expressed scepticism over net
OL,10,Fzero, it says.
OL,12,FAnd the report warns that the new
OL,13,FLabour Government has only fully put
OL,14,Fin place measures to meet one of the
OL,15,F10 priority recommendations for this
OL,16,Fyear, on renewable power auctions, and
OL,17,Fpartly in place for four, such as
OL,18,Flifting planning barriers to heat
OL,19,Fpumps and wind, and reversing policy
OL,20,Frollbacks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
