OL,3,CCall for fair, ambitious climate plan
OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,FThat is despite business leaders
OL,7,Fsaying the climate targets provide
OL,8,Fcertainty for investment and driving
OL,9,Fgrowth and innovation.
OL,11,FFormer Climate Change Committee
OL,12,Fchairman Lord Deben said the Climate
OL,13,FChange Act has forced ministers to pay
OL,14,Fmore attention to this "existential
OL,15,Fissue", but "substandard" plans were
OL,16,Fproduced by the previous government.
