OL,3,CCall for fair, ambitious climate plan
OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,F"The plan which this new Government
OL,7,Fmust produce has to show clearly how
OL,8,Fwe reach net zero by 2050 and put us
OL,9,Fback on track to meeting legally
OL,10,Fbinding commitments," he said.
OL,12,F"If it fails to do so, the negative
OL,13,Fimplications for the international
OL,14,Fclimate regime and for business
OL,15,Fconfidence will be severe."
OL,17,FFriends of the Earth campaigner Danny
OL,18,FGross said following domestic
OL,19,Fpolitical setbacks and an escalating
OL,20,Fclimate crisis, the UK Government
OL,21,Furgently needs to show real leadership.
