OL,3,CCall for fair, ambitious climate plan
OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,F"Keir Starmer's pledge to cut UK
OL,7,Femissions by 81% by 2035 was a welcome
OL,8,Fmove towards rebuilding this country's
OL,9,Ftarnished reputation. Now we need an
OL,10,Fambitious climate action plan to
OL,11,Fensure this target is met in a way
OL,12,Fthat ensure everyone benefits from a
OL,13,Ffair transition to a zero-carbon
OL,14,Feconomy," he said.
OL,16,F"This will also boost energy security,
OL,17,Flower bills and give businesses the
OL,18,Fconfidence to invest in the green
OL,19,Feconomy and create new jobs."
