OL,4,Cas UK emissions-cutting targets at risk
OL,6,FEnergy Secretary Ed Miliband said:
OL,7,F"Climate action is critical for
OL,8,Fnational security, which is why our
OL,9,Fmission for clean power will provide
OL,10,Fhomegrown energy, protect billpayers
OL,11,Fand boost the UK's energy independence.
OL,13,F"Our ambitious and pragmatic new
OL,14,Ftarget to reduce emissions by 81% by
OL,15,F2035 builds on the legacy of the
OL,16,FClimate Change Act, supporting the
OL,17,FUK's mission for growth and helping to
OL,18,Fattract further investment and jobs in
OL,19,Flow carbon technologies.
